### DeliveryNote Endpoints Testing File

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@projectId = PROJECT_ID_HERE
@deliveryNoteId = DELIVERY_NOTE_ID_HERE
@clientId = CLIENT_ID_HERE

---

## DELIVERY NOTES CRUD

### 1. Crear albarán de horas - POST /api/deliverynote
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "description": "Trabajo realizado en obra",
  "date": "2024-05-15T10:30:00Z",
  "format": "hours",
  "hours": 8,
  "workers": [
    {
      "name": "Juan García",
      "hours": 4
    },
    {
      "name": "María López",
      "hours": 4
    }
  ]
}

### 2. Crear albarán de material - POST /api/deliverynote
POST {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{projectId}}",
  "description": "Entrega de materiales",
  "date": "2024-05-15T14:00:00Z",
  "format": "material",
  "material": "Cemento Portland 42.5",
  "quantity": 50,
  "unit": "sacos"
}

### 3. Listar albaranes - GET /api/deliverynote
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4. Listar albaranes con filtro por proyecto
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&project={{projectId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5. Listar albaranes con filtro por cliente
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&client={{clientId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 6. Listar albaranes con filtro por formato
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&format=hours
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 7. Listar solo albaranes firmados
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&signed=true
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 8. Listar albaranes por rango de fechas
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 9. Listar albaranes ordenados por fecha descendente
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote?page=1&limit=10&sort=-workDate
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 10. Obtener albarán específico - GET /api/deliverynote/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 11. Descargar albarán en PDF - GET /api/deliverynote/pdf/:id
GET {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/pdf/{{deliveryNoteId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 12. Firmar albarán - PATCH /api/deliverynote/:id/sign
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}}/sign
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="signature"; filename="firma.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./uploads/firma.png
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 13. Archivar albarán (soft delete) - DELETE /api/deliverynote/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}}?soft=true
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 14. Eliminar albarán permanentemente (hard delete) - DELETE /api/deliverynote/:id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deliverynote/{{deliveryNoteId}}?soft=false
Authorization: {{authToken}}
